| Title Hero | Inter | 72px | 700 | 1.2 | -3% |
| Title Page | Inter | 48px | 700 | 1.2 | -2% |
| Subtitle | Inter | 32px | 400 | 1.2 | — |
| Heading | Inter | 24px | 600 | 1.2 | -2% |
| Subheading | Inter | 20px | 400 | 1.2 | — |
| Body Base | Inter | 16px | 400 | 1.4 | — |
| Body Strong | Inter | 16px | 600 | 1.4 | — |
| Body Emphasis | Inter | 400 | italic | 1.4 | — |
| Body Link | Inter | 16px | 400 | 1.4 | — |
| Body Small | Inter | 14px | 400 | 1.4 | — |
| Body Small Strong | Inter | 14px | 600 | 1.4 | — |
| Body Code | Roboto Mono | 16px | 400 | 1.3 | — |
| Single Line/Body Base | Inter | 16px | 400 | 1.0 | — |
| Single Line/Body Small Strong | Inter | 14px | 600 | 1.0 | — |
| Cover Display | Whyte | 188px | 400 | 0.9 | -2% |

## Colors

```css
--color-black:       #000000;
--color-white:       #FFFFFF;
--color-blue:        #4D49FC;
--color-cyan:        #00B6FF;
--color-green:       #24CB71;
--color-purple:      #874FFF;
--color-coral:       #FF7676;
--color-red:         #FF3737;
```

IMPORTANT: Never hardcode hex values — always use CSS variables above.

## Shadows

```css
--shadow-300: 0px 4px 4px -1px rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.05), 0px 4px 4px -1px rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.1);
```

## Border Radius

- Buttons / pills: `200px`
- Cards / panels: `40px`
- Small elements: `8px`

## Components in Figma

Accordion, AI Chat, Avatars, Buttons, Calendar, Cards, Dialog, Inputs, Menu, Navigation, Notification, Pagination, Tabs, Tags, Text, Tooltip, Forms, Sections.

