## atpc.world — Current State

- `index.html` — fullscreen video (`atpcintro.mp4`), after video ends → ATPC text fades in
- `style.css` — dark, minimal, overflow hidden
- `script.js` — listens for `video.ended`, adds `.visible` class

## Figma Workflow

When implementing from Figma:
1. Use `get_figma_data(fileKey, nodeId)` to get design context
2. Use `download_figma_images` for assets
3. Translate to plain HTML/CSS/JS (no frameworks unless requested)
4. Match typography and colors exactly from this design system
5. Validate visually against Figma
